# Keep GitHub source downloads (Code > Download ZIP, release tarballs) to only
# the files needed to RUN FieldKit. Everything is export-ignored, then the two
# runtime files are re-included. Dev/meta files stay in the repo for
# contributors but never ship in a download. (git archive honors these.)
* export-ignore
/FieldKit.html   -export-ignore
/library-data.js -export-ignore
